			<p>
			“We arrive from the mountains to the desert to flatten it by hand.<br>
			During the day there was no wind and during the night,
			<br>a darkness blacker than any other.<br>
			
			Then, we used to put cans with oil under each leg of the bed<br>
			to drown the vermin that try to climb them.<br>
			
			That’s why I like the smell of oil.”</p>
		</div>
