	<div class="intro-text">
		<p>In a empty room stands a wooden bed supported by 4 glass jars on the legs, each containing a single poisonous vermin. The inverted jars are open, only the weight of the bed is preventing the animals from escaping.</p>
		<p>For the layout of the space we use the concept of <em>disassemble</em> and we remove every item in the room, the closet, the curtains, the light switch, everything.</p>
	</div>
